      <title>阿根廷油田亿万富翁对 Milei 抱有“很大的希望”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/argentina-s-oilfield-billionaire-tells-ceraweek-he-has-lot-of-hope-for-milei</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油管制造商泰纳里斯公司(Tenaris SA)亿万富翁首席执行官保罗·罗卡(Paolo Rocca)表示，人们对阿根廷总统哈维尔·米雷(Javier Milei)能够推动该国页岩矿床的开发抱有很高的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/argentina-s-oilfield-billionaire-tells-ceraweek-he-has-lot-of-hope-for-milei</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:38:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储将维持当前缩减资产负债表的节奏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/fed-will-maintain-current-cadence-of-reducing-its-balance-sheet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使过剩的流动性继续从金融体系中流失，美联储仍将维持减持债券的步伐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/fed-will-maintain-current-cadence-of-reducing-its-balance-sheet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:17:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储向市场保证 2024 年降息，短期债券上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/bonds-rally-after-fed-keeps-2024-median-rate-forecast-at-3-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储政策制定者坚持今年降息三个百分点的预测后，短期国债大幅上涨，消除了市场对美联储将遏制宽松货币政策计划的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/bonds-rally-after-fed-keeps-2024-median-rate-forecast-at-3-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:13:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克对叛军密谋反对他表示愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/sunak-expresses-anger-with-rebel-tories-over-plots-against-him</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，里希·苏纳克告诉保守党成员，叛乱议员让他“愤怒”，这表明总理认为他需要反击推翻他的阴谋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/sunak-expresses-anger-with-rebel-tories-over-plots-against-him</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:46:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称中国有望在 2027 年做好入侵台湾的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/china-on-track-to-be-ready-for-taiwan-invasion-by-2027-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位美国高级海军上将作证说，中国正在以二战以来从未有过的规模建设其军事和核武库，所有迹象都表明中国正在坚持到 2027 年入侵台湾的野心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/china-on-track-to-be-ready-for-taiwan-invasion-by-2027-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰立法者指责央行行长债券购买失误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/polish-lawmakers-accuse-central-bank-chief-of-bond-buying-faults</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克所在政党的议员将对该国央行行长提出一系列冗长的指控，作为最终寻求罢免行长亚当·格拉平斯基的动议的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/polish-lawmakers-accuse-central-bank-chief-of-bond-buying-faults</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:26:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥官员称萨利纳斯集团欠债 38 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/salinas-companies-owe-3-8-billion-mexican-tax-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国税务机关负责人周三表示，里卡多·萨利纳斯·普列戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 控制的四家公司欠政府 630 亿比索（合 38 亿美元），总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔 (Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador) 与这位亿万富翁之间的争端日益加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/salinas-companies-owe-3-8-billion-mexican-tax-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:52:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登关于汽车排放的最新规定将促进电动汽车销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/biden-set-to-boost-electric-car-sales-with-new-epa-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府周三采取行动，遏制美国汽车和轻型卡车的污染，实行严格的尾气排放限制，这将迫使汽车制造商迅速提高电池电动和插电式混合动力车型的销量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/biden-set-to-boost-electric-car-sales-with-new-epa-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普法官允许对其对检察官威利斯罗曼史的裁决提出上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trump-judge-allows-appeal-of-his-ruling-on-fani-willis-romance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和几名共同被告获准对佐治亚州法官的裁决提出上诉，该裁决称富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯尽管与一名高级检察官有恋情，但仍可以继续参与州选举干预案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trump-judge-allows-appeal-of-his-ruling-on-fani-willis-romance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰总理预计美国最早将于本月提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ukrainian-premier-sees-us-aid-coming-as-early-as-this-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总理表示，美国受阻的资金最早可能在本月到达，而且为前线招募新兵的规模可能少于军方最初支持的 50 万人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/ukrainian-premier-sees-us-aid-coming-as-early-as-this-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
